short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Lets you create any element you want in Infinite Craft.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You can also use it to back up your saves and import any save.

Changelog:
Version 1.0.1
-Added a "Remove element" button, letting you remove any element from the game, even those that weren't added by this extension.

-Release
-Create any element
